[I] Concurrent, cache-efficient, and Dockerfile-agnostic builder toolkit

[T] BuildKit is a toolkit for converting source code to build artifacts in an
[T] efficient, expressive and repeatable manner.

[U] https://github.com/moby/buildkit

[A] Buildkit Authors
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/base

[L] APL
[V] 0.28.1

[D] fbb07de27d2578043f2bc337446ada84f9e12023c02775b4a1252c03 buildkit-0.28.1.tar.gz https://github.com/moby/buildkit/archive/refs/tags/v0.28.1/

. $base/package/*/*/go-conf.in

hook_add premake 5 'mkdir -p objs'
var_append goconfopt ' ' '-o objs ./cmd/buildctl ./cmd/buildkitd'
hook_add postmake 5 'cp -vf objs/* $root$bindir/'
